Reliance Industries Shares Gain in Mumbai Trading

-- B y   J o h n   C h a c k o
-- 
2011-10-19T03:49:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/reliance-industries-shares-gain-in-mumbai-trading.html
Reliance Industries Ltd. (RIL)  gained 0.7
percent to 825.90 rupees at 9:17 a.m. in Mumbai trading, after
climbing as much as 0.9 percent.  The Securities and Exchange Board of  India  may ask Reliance
to pay as much as 20.5 billion rupees to settle charges of
 insider trading , the Mint newspaper reported today. Reliance
spokesman  Manoj Warrier  and N. Hariharan, a spokesman for the
capital markets regulator, declined to comment on the report.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Chacko at 
 jchacko@bloomberg.net  